00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:22.000
So how do we introduce time lags
into the logistic?

00:17:22.000 --> 00:17:28.000
Well, the simplest way is to
introduce time.  So, we're

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:37.000
going to say dNt/dt.
